API Automation Question

API response:
{
  "id":101,
  "name":"Saddam",
  "email":"saddam@test.com",
  "address":{
      "city":"Pune",
      "country":"India"
  }
}
Using Rest Assured + Java:

1. Validate status code = 200
2. Validate city = "Pune"
3. Validate email contains "@test.com"
---------------------------------------------
1. Assert.assertEqual(response.statusCode(), 200);
2. JsonPath jpath = response.jsonPath();
    Assert.assertEquals(jpath.getString("address.city"), "Pune");
3.  Assert.assertTrue(jpath.getString("email").contains("@test.com"));
